4 Section 5. That § 4-7-39 be REPEALED.
5 The commissioner of the Bureau of Finance and Management shall transfer any
6 unobligated cash remaining after the transfer into the budget reserve fund as required by
7 § 4-7-32 into the general revenue replacement fund if the amount in the general revenue
8 replacement fund does not exceed fifteen percent of the general fund appropriations in
9 the General Appropriations Act for the previous fiscal year.
